# format
snippet b "bold" b
**${0:${VISUAL}}**
endsnippet
snippet 粗 "bold" b
**${0:${VISUAL}}**
endsnippet
snippet 粗体 "bold" b
**${0:${VISUAL}}**
endsnippet
snippet 黑 "bold" b
**${0:${VISUAL}}**
endsnippet
snippet 黑体 "bold" b
