endsnippet
snippet 粗斜 "bold italic" b
***${0:${VISUAL}}***
endsnippet
snippet 黑斜 "bold italic" b
***${0:${VISUAL}}***
endsnippet
snippet 粗斜体 "bold italic" b
***${0:${VISUAL}}***
endsnippet

