endsnippet
snippet 注释 "comment"
<!-- ${0:${VISUAL}} -->
endsnippet

# line
snippet ln "line" b
---
${0}
endsnippet
snippet 分隔线 "line" b
---
${0}
endsnippet
snippet d "del line"
~~${0:${VISUAL}}~~
endsnippet
snippet 删除 "del line"
~~${0:${VISUAL}}~~
endsnippet
